OL,6,GSwansea Hackspace is a community-run
OL,7,Gspace in Swansea where enthusiasts in
OL,8,Gelectronics, textiles, science,
OL,9,Gdigital art, crafting and just hacking
OL,10,Gon stuff can meet, share, learn, and
OL,11,Gwork. A bunch of us will be attending
OL,12,GEMF as a village, and we may have some
OL,13,Ginteresting projects to show off! Come
OL,14,Gand say hello!
OL,22,D]CEMFFAX: The world at your fingertips\
